#: en/installation-and-basic-configuration.xml:312
#| msgid ""
#| "If your web server is running with the same user rights as OTRS, the "
#| "command to set the proper access rights is <command>otrs.SetPermissions."
#| "pl /opt/otrs --otrs-user=otrs --web-user=otrs</command>. On SUSE systems "
#| "the web server is running with the user rights of wwwrun. On Debian-based "
#| "systems this is www-data. You would use the command <command>otrs."
#| "SetPermissions.pl /opt/otrs --otrs-user=otrs --web-user=wwwrun --otrs-"
