#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:516
#| msgid ""
#| "Through the link \"Queue\" of the admin area, you can manage the <link "
#| "linkend=\"what-is-a-queue\"> queues </link> of your system (see Figure "
#| "5.18 below). In a new OTRS installation there are 4 default queues: Junk, "
#| "Misc, Postmaster and Raw. All incoming messages will be stored in it the "
