#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:1779
#| msgid ""
#| "Using the \"Package Manager\" in the admin area, you can install and "
#| "manage packages that extend the functionality of OTRS (see Figure 5.58 "
#| "below). See the <link linkend=\"application\">Additional applications</"
#| "link> section for a discussion on the extensions that are available from "
#| "the OTRS repositories."
