msgstr "Настройки Задания"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/performance-tuning.xml:135
#| msgid ""
#| "Provide a name for the archiving job and select proper options to "
#| "schedule this job."
msgid "Provide a name for the archiving job, and select proper options to schedule this job."
msgstr "Введите имя для работы архивирования, и выберите надлежащие опции для планирования этой работы."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/performance-tuning.xml:140
msgid "Ticket Filter"
msgstr "Ticket Filter"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/performance-tuning.xml:143
#| msgid ""
#| "The ticket filter is basically a ticket search that is looking for "
#| "tickets that match the selected criteria.  It might be a good idea to "
#| "only archive tickets in a close state that have been closed a few months "
#| "before."
msgid "The ticket filter is searches for tickets that match the selected criteria. It might be a good idea to only archive those tickets in a closed state that have been closed a few months before."
msgstr "Фильтр заявок производит поиск заявок, которые отвечают выбраным критериям. Хорошей идеей будет заархивировать закрытые заявки, которые были закрыты за несколько месяцев до этого."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/performance-tuning.xml:148
msgid "Ticket Action"
msgstr "Действия над заявками"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/performance-tuning.xml:151
#| msgid ""
#| "In the section Ticket Action you will find an action called \"Archive "
#| "selected tickets\".  Set this to \"archive tickets\"."
msgid "In this section, set the field labeled \"Archive selected tickets\" to \"archive tickets\"."
msgstr "В этой части установите поле \"Архивировать выбранные заявки\" в \"архив заявок\"."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/performance-tuning.xml:156
