#: en/performance-tuning.xml:175
msgid "Ticket Search"
msgstr "Поиск Заявок"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/performance-tuning.xml:178
#| msgid ""
#| "When you search for tickets, the system default is only searching tickets "
#| "which are not archived.  If you want to search through archived tickets "
#| "also, simply add \"archive search\" while defining search criteria."
msgid "When you search for tickets, the system default is to search tickets which are not archived. If you want to search through archived tickets also, simply add \"archive search\" while defining search criteria."
msgstr "При поиске заявок, система по умолчанию производит поиск среди не архивированных заявок. Установите критерий поиска \"поиск в архивах\", если нужно чтобы поиск происходил также и в архивированых заявках."

