#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/performance-tuning.xml:285
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have a really large installation (over 1,000 new tickets per day "
#| "and over 40 agents) it is a good idea to read \"Choosing the Right "
